NI DUNG TM TT
1. L do chn ti
Hin nay h thng qun l nng lng (EMS) ang tr ln ph bin, phc v
cho khng ch cc ta nh m c cc h gia nh, thm ch c cc mng in nh
(microgrid). i vi cc h thng quy m nh v va HEMS (Home Energy
Management System) hoc BEMS (Building Management System) th c th dng
chung h tng CNTT gim chi ph vn hnh v chi ph u t ban u, thm ch
c th dng di dng dch v thay cho vic u t c h thng y .
l c s cho vic pht trin cc ng dng qun l nng lng trn nn in
ton m my.
y l mt xu hng m th gii ang tp trung nghin cu pht trin.
2. Mc ch nghin cu ca lun vn, i tng, phm vi nghin cu
2.1 Mc ch nghin cu ca lun vn
Xy dng mt h thng qun l nng lng trn nn in ton m my, c kh
nng qun l c lng in nng tiu th ca cc ti, pht hin ra lng ph nng
lng, d on nhu cu nng lng, nhn dng ti, ti u ha chi ph v nng
lng.
2
2.2 i tng v phm vi nghin cu
L thuyt QLNL v in ton m my, thit k & xy dng h thng cung cp
dch v qun l nng lng da trn nn tng in ton m my. o c kt qu
v nh gi hiu nng hot ng ca h thng.
3. Ni dung chnh ca lun vn v ng gp ca tc gi
Chng 1: Nghin cu v Qun l nng lng v in ton m my. Gii
thiu chung v h thng QLNL v in ton m my, cc m hnh QLNL v in
ton m my ang c s dng. Xu hng cng ngh th gii vi nn tng thng
minh S.M.A.C v cng ngh o ha ca Micosoft.
Chng 2: Thit k h thng Qun l nng lng. Thit k v xy dng kin
trc h thng QLNL s dng cng ngh in ton m my theo hng S.M.A.C
cho php cung cp dch v QLNL, c chc nng gim st, iu khin v qun l cc
thit b in t xa qua mng Internet
Chng 3: Xy dng h thng Qun l nng lng trn nn in ton m
my. Tch hp h thng QLNL vo h thng in ton m my ca Microsoft.
Chng 4: Kt qu nghin cu v nh gia. Thit lp h thng th nghim
gm cc sn phm phn cng kt ni vi h thng phn mm qun l nng lng
trn nn in ton m my thng qua mi trng mng TCP/IP hn hp (khng
dy & c dy) v cc ti. nh gi hiu nng v tin cy ca h thng truyn
thng v mc chu ti ca h thng QLNL.
4. Kt lun
Qua thi gian nghin cu, cc ng gp ca hc vin trong lun vn l :
- Xy dng h tng S.M.A.C phc v cho QLNL
